## Tokenomics (NXK)

**Total Supply:** 21,000,000 NXK  
**Staking:** Not included (no staking program)

### Allocation
| Category | Percent | Amount (NXK) | Notes |
|---|---:|---:|---|
| Liquidity Pool (DEX / Uniswap) | 45% | 9,450,000 | Liquidity may be added in phases |
| Ecosystem Fund (Future Expansion) | 20% | 4,200,000 | Utility, integrations, grants, audits/bug bounties, ecosystem growth |
| Team & Development | 15% | 3,150,000 | **24-month cliff + 12-month linear vesting** |
| Marketing & Partnerships | 10% | 2,100,000 | Growth campaigns, partnerships (governed + transparent) |
| Airdrop & Community Incentives | 5% | 1,050,000 | Early supporters, incentives, adoption programs |
| Advisors | 5% | 1,050,000 | **24-month cliff + 12-month linear vesting** |

### Ecosystem Fund
Not subject to linear vesting. Managed via multisig governance and spent based on project milestones. All transfers are publicly disclosed for transparency.

### Vesting Summary
- **Team & Development:** 24-month cliff, then released linearly over 12 months  
- **Advisors:** 24-month cliff, then released linearly over 12 months  

### Treasury / Governance Transparency (Recommended Policy)
- Ecosystem and Marketing wallets should be controlled by **Safe (multisig) + Timelock** (or an equivalent public-delay policy).
- Spending should be **milestone-based** (deliverable â†’ tranche release).
- Publish a **monthly transparency log**: amount, destination address, reason, and transaction link.
